Method: POST
URL: /api/basic/tenants/{tenantId}/alerts/{alertId}/actions/{action}

Example:
/api/basic/tenants/{tenantId}/alerts/{alertId}/actions/acknowledge
/api/basic/tenants/{tenantId}/alerts/{alertId}/actions/suppress
/api/basic/tenants/{tenantId}/alerts/{alertId}/actions/permanentSuppress
/api/basic/tenants/{tenantId}/alerts/{alertId}/actions/close
 
Headers:
	Authorization : Basic c3N2Ok5ldCF0aXZhbW81YjY=
	Content-Type : application/json
	Accept : application/json 
	
Request Payload:
	{
		"description": "My comment"
	}

Response Code: 200 OK
 
Note: Encode username and password with colon(:) in between using Base64 algorithm.
base64_encode(loginName:password). Include this with 'Basic' prefix in Authorization header.